TableContextTimeStampBeforeTable: {2710=So sorry to report that there is no Folk Espresso this morning....mainly because there appears to be no electricity at the station.  I showed up at 5:15 with a sackful of great music, but alas, the place was a ghost-town.  The night's wind and rain must've done quite a number on some electrical box somewhere!  Well, be sure to tune in tomorrow morning for Early Morning Gumbo with Diane Karl--she always does a terrific show.  And I'll be back next Monday...}

textBeforeTable: 10/24/2010 Air date:  Music Without Borders Program name:  Eclectic Categories: Music Without Borders playlist for 10/24/2010 Login or register to post comments Diane Hunt Warmly, So sorry to report that there is no Folk Espresso this morning....mainly because there appears to be no electricity at the station.  I showed up at 5:15 with a sackful of great music, but alas, the place was a ghost-town.  The night's wind and rain must've done quite a number on some electrical box somewhere!  Well, be sure to tune in tomorrow morning for Early Morning Gumbo with Diane Karl--she always does a terrific show.  And I'll be back next Monday...
